Following his big win at the Grammy’s last night, Nigerian star, Burna Boy took to Instagram to celebrate! We can see the Grammy winner dancing with friends and family out in the open. View this post on Instagram A post shared by Olorisupergal (@olorisupergal) Burna Boy bagged the award as the ‘Best Global Music’ category at the 63rd Grammys award with his album, ‘Twice as Tall‘. The recording academy made the announcement via their official page on Twitter. “Congrats Best Global Music Album winner – ‘TWICE AS TALL’ @burnaboy #GRAMMYs,” the tweet read. Congrats Burna! More Wins!